flowchart TD
    A["User asks to share screen"] --> B["Voice tool / reply pipeline<br/>offer_screen_share_link"]
    B --> C["ScreenShareSessionManager.createSession()<br/>token + share URL"]
    C --> D["Share page /share/:token<br/>capture loop every keyframeIntervalMs"]
    D --> E["POST /api/voice/share-session/:token/frame"]

    E --> F["Latest frame buffer"]
    E --> G{"brainContextEnabled?"}
    G -->|yes| H["Background scanner<br/>note + sceneChanged"]
    H --> I["Rolling temporal notes"]

    F --> J["Normal voice brain turn"]
    I --> J
    J --> K["Speak or [SKIP]"]

    F --> L{"Autonomous commentary enabled?"}
    H --> L
    L -->|first frame / silence /\nscene change when scanner runs| J

    I --> M["Session recap on share end"]
    M --> N["One-line memory fact"]
